{{Politics of Benin}}

The '''Alliance for a Triumphant Benin''' ({{lang-fr|Alliance pour un Bénin Triomphant}}, ABT) is a [[political alliance]] in [[Benin]] led by [[Abdoulaye Bio Tchané]].

==History==
The alliance received 3.7% of the vote in the [[Beninese parliamentary election, 2015|2015 parliamentary elections]], winning two seats.<ref>[http://www.24haubenin.info/?+Les-FCBE-arrivent-en-tete-du+ Les FCBE arrivent en tête du scrutin législatif avec 32 sièges] 24 Heures, 2 May 2015</ref>

